video_title: What do you resonate most about this short? #mindset #shorts #advice #overthinking
transcript:
these are four quotes to help you stop
overthinking
number one you cannot get what you want
if you don't stop thinking about what
you don't want
number two dwelling and worrying about
difficulties does not solve them
planning and taking action does
number three when you notice yourself
worrying about what could go wrong
remind yourself to get excited about
what could go right
and number four let life be what it
needs to be not what you want it to be
